## Interface: 30300
## Title: Looty
## Notes: Tracks group loot and master loot rolls in a compact window.
## Author: Ravelo
## Version: 2.0.0
## SavedVariables: Looty_SavedVars

## Load order:
##   1. Locale     — strings and patterns (no Looty reference)
##   2. Domain     — GroupLoot, MasterLoot (reference Looty inside functions only)
##   3. UI         — Primitives, tab renderers, Frame (same)
##   4. Parser     — chat message routing (same)
##   5. Core       — LAST: creates LootyCore frame, sets global Looty,
##                   registers events. By this point all modules are defined.
##                   No module references Looty at file load time.

Locales\enUS.lua

GroupLoot.lua
MasterLoot.lua

UI\Primitives.lua
UI\GroupLootUI.lua
UI\MasterLootUI.lua
UI\Frame.lua

Parser.lua
Core.lua
